short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get a wrapped of your Yale Hospitality history for the Fall 2024 semester!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides you with a simple "wrapped" of your Yale Hospitality history! Simply go to Yale's transact campus page (https://yale-sp.transactcampus.com/eAccounts/BoardTransaction.aspx) to generate your wrapped. 

Yale's transact campus page: https://yale-sp.transactcampus.com/eAccounts/BoardTransaction.aspx
